{
  "id": "640d56dfaa9f1e001c3b8a40",
  "title": "和積の公式の問題をオイラーの公式で解く",
  "created": 1678595808,
  "updated": 1683520041,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "640d56dfaa9f1e001c3b8a40",
      "text": "和積の公式の問題をオイラーの公式で解く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74d3",
      "text": "from [@yuyasurarin]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74d4",
      "text": "和積の公式の問題をオイラーの公式で解く",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74d5",
      "text": "[/yuyasurarin/和積の公式の問題を解く]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74d6",
      "text": " [オイラーの公式]を使うと機械的に導出できたりします",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74d7",
      "text": "   [積和公式]および[和積公式]も同様",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74d8",
      "text": "  [$ 4\\cos\\frac A2\\cos\\frac B2\\cos\\frac C2]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74d9",
      "text": "   [$ =4\\Re e^{i\\frac A2}\\Re e^{i\\frac B2}\\Re e^{i\\frac C2}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74da",
      "text": "    [$ \\Re z:=\\frac{z+\\bar{z}}{2}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74db",
      "text": "     複素数の実部を取り出す関数",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d572daff09e00006f74ea",
      "text": "     [オイラーの公式#626f95741280f00000cca005]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595888,
      "updated": 1678595888
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74dc",
      "text": "   [$ =4\\cdot\\frac{e^{i\\frac A2}+e^{-i\\frac A2}}{2}\\frac{e^{i\\frac B2}+e^{-i\\frac B2}}{2}\\frac{e^{i\\frac C2}+e^{-i\\frac C2}}{2}]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74dd",
      "text": "   [$ =\\frac12\\left(e^{i\\frac{A+B}{2}}+e^{-i\\frac{A+B}{2}}+e^{i\\frac{A-B}{2}}+e^{i\\frac{-(A-B)}{2}}\\right)\\left(e^{i\\frac C2}+e^{-i\\frac C2}\\right)]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74de",
      "text": "   [$ =\\frac12\\left(e^{i\\frac{A+B+C}{2}}+e^{-i\\frac{A+B+C}{2}}+e^{i\\frac{A-B+C}{2}}+e^{i\\frac{-(A-B+C)}{2}}+e^{i\\frac{A+B-C}{2}}+e^{i\\frac{-(A+B-C)}{2}}+e^{i\\frac{A-B-C}{2}}+e^{i\\frac{-(A-B-C)}{2}}\\right)]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74df",
      "text": "    ここまで、展開しただけ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74e0",
      "text": "   [$ =\\cos\\frac12(A+B+C)+\\cos\\frac12(A-B+C)+\\cos\\frac12(A+B-C)+\\cos\\frac12(A-B-C)]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "64587a1e1280f000005829d5",
      "text": "    ここまでは任意の[$ A,B,C]で成立する",
      "userId": "5ef2bdebb60650001e1280f0",
      "created": 1683520031,
      "updated": 1683520041
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74e1",
      "text": "   [$ =0+\\cos\\left(\\frac\\pi2-B\\right)+\\cos\\left(\\frac\\pi2-C\\right)+\\cos\\left(A-\\frac\\pi2\\right)] ",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74e2",
      "text": "    [$ \\because A+B+C=\\pi]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74e3",
      "text": "   [$ = \\sin B+\\sin C+\\sin A]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74e4",
      "text": "   [$ \\underline{= \\sin A+\\sin B+\\sin C\\quad}_\\blacksquare]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74e5",
      "text": " [- なんもわからん！！！[yuyasurarin.icon][Mijinko_SD.icon]]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74e6",
      "text": " ([初心者に対する説明]として非常に不適切なコメントなので@に書かないほうがいいと思っていたが、このメモを書いていたページを掃除していた際に行き場所が見つからず、とりあえずここに供養した次第です。わからなくても心配しないでください[takker.icon])",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
    {
      "id": "640d56deaff09e00006f74e7",
      "text": "  公式を調べに行ったらいつかは理解できるようになる...かも[yuyasurarin.icon]",
      "userId": "582e63d27c56960011aff09e",
      "created": 1678595808,
      "updated": 1678595808
    },
